defaultNorman Bakerdefault: I have mentioned some of the actions already that the Home Secretary has taken as a consequence of that.  HMIC clearly went away to do further work and revisited 13 forces to dig further into that.  There was an understanding that although a green light had been given, 
defaultfurther
