defaultQ541 default&#xa0; 
defaultPaul Flynn:default On the basis of the evidence that we have, why do you think the police appear to be recording a 
defaultlower
default proportion of crimes reported to them than in previous years?
defaultNorman Bakerdefault: Do you mean why is there divergence from the Crime Survey for 
defaultEngland
default and 
defaultWales
