defaultQ587 default&#xa0; 
defaultMr Turner:default What 
defaultwill
default you do differently in the future to ensure good crime statistics?
defaultNorman Bakerdefault: That partly depends on what HMIC produce by way of their report.  If they identify systemic failures across all forces or a large number of forces as a consequence of particular processes, for example, then those processes will have to be changed, if they are generating those 
defaultunwelcome
